CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1961, pg. 20 reads: "Hail, Hail, The Gang's All Here! - Newsboys, girls, and distributors pose for Courier lensman, Teenie Harris, at South Park's Sully's Grove. More than 150 braved the elements to take part in the festivities at the annual Courier Newsboys' Picnic, Aug. 25."
TitMainTitle: Group of young men and boys, including young boy wearing dark striped button down collared shirt, gathered on field in South Park for the annual Pittsburgh Courier Newsboys' Picnic
